<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="increase-n">increase <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'ɪŋkriːs/    美 /'ɪŋkriːs/  </p>
<p>[C] &amp; [U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>增加；增长：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>price / tax increase</strong>
价格 / 税收上涨</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Not only do the nurses want a pay increase, they want reduced hours as well.
护士们不仅想要涨工资，还想要减少工作时间。</p><footer>2014 全国</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="on-the-increase">on the increase</h3>
<p>1.<strong>在增加：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>A few years ago it was an endangered species, but now the population is on the increase. 
几年前，它还是濒临灭绝的物种，但现在它们的数量在不断增加。</p><footer> 外研⑤ – 6</footer></div></div>